<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT40">
<l>veṟpeṉṟu vēṅkaṭam pāṭiṉēṉ vīṭākki</l>
<l>niṟkiṉṟē ṉiṉṟu niṉaikkiṉṟēṉ kaṟkiṉṟa</l>
<l>nūlvalaiyiṟ paṭṭirunta nūlāṭṭi kēḷvaṉār</l>
<l>kālvalaiyiṟ paṭṭiruntēṉ kāṇ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I sang of Vēṅkaṭam thinking it is [the name of] a mountain.</l>
<l>I [thus] stand having arranged for liberation. I stand thinking [about this].</l>
<l>I remain caught in the nets that are the feet of the Husband of the Lady of the Vedas,</l>
<l>Who [Himself] remains caught in the nets that are the Vedas that are learned, see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
